          '\\E4%{64}%?%p1%t%{65}%|%;%?%p2%t%{66}%|%;%?%p3%t%{65}%|%;%?%p4%t%{68}%|%;%?%p5%t%{64}%|%;%?%p6%t%{72}%|%;%?%p7%t%{80}%|%;%c%?%p9%t\\E>A%e\\E>B%;' => '
#
# Stub version of: \\E4%{64}%?%p1%t%{65}%|%;%?%p2%t%{66}%|%;%?%p3%t%{65}%|%;%?%p4%t%{68}%|%;%?%p5%t%{64}%|%;%?%p6%t%{72}%|%;%?%p7%t%{80}%|%;%c%?%p9%t\\E>A%e\\E>B%;
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "4"; # 4
  push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 65); # %{65}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 66); # %{66}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 65); # %{65}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 68); # %{68}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 72); # %{72}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 80); # %{80}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\>"; # >
    $rc .= "A"; # A
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\>"; # >
    $rc .= "B"; # B
  } # %;

  return $rc;
}
',

#
# Stub version of: \\E[=%?%p1%{0}%=%t0m%e%p1%{1}%=%t4m%e%p1%{2}%=%t3m%e%p1%{3}%=%t5m%e%p1%{4}%=%t2m%e%p1%{5}%=%t6m%e%p1%{6}%=%t7m%e1m%;
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  $rc .= "\\="; # =
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "0"; # 0
    $rc .= "m"; # m
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
    $rc .= "m"; # m
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "3"; # 3
    $rc .= "m"; # m
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 3); # %{3}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
    $rc .= "m"; # m
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "2"; # 2
    $rc .= "m"; # m
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 5); # %{5}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "6"; # 6
    $rc .= "m"; # m

              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 6); # %{6}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "7"; # 7
    $rc .= "m"; # m
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "1"; # 1
    $rc .= "m"; # m
  } # %;

  return $rc;

#
# Stub version of: \\036B%p1%?%p1%{8}%<%t%{2}%&%?%p1%{1}%&%t%{4}%|%;%?%p1%{4}%&%t%{1}%|%;%;%{48}%+%c

  $rc .= chr(oct(36)); # \\036
  $rc .= "B"; # B
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
    if (do { # %?
             push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
             push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
             push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
             pop(@iparam);
           }) { # %t
      push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
      push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
    } # %;
    if (do { # %?
             push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
             push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
             push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
             pop(@iparam);
           }) { # %t
      push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
      push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
    } # %;
  } # %;
  push(@iparam, 48); # %{48}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c

  return $rc;

  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E

  $rc .= "\\?"; # ?

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1

              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "2"; # 2
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x - $y); } # %-
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  } # %;
  $rc .= "m"; # m

  return $rc;
}
',

#
# Stub version of: %p1%{8}%/%{6}%*%{4}%+\\E[%d%p1%{8}%m%Pa%?%ga%{1}%=%t4%e%ga%{3}%=%t6%e%ga%{4}%=%t1%e%ga%{6}%=%t3%e%ga%d%;m

  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $y ? int($x / $y) : 0); } # %/
  push(@iparam, 6); # %{6}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) * pop(@iparam)); # %*
  push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $y ? int($x % $y) : 0); } # %m
  $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
           push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
              push(@iparam, 3); # %{3}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "6"; # 6
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
              push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "1"; # 1
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
              push(@iparam, 6); # %{6}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "3"; # 3
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga

         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[7]); # %p8
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\)"; # )
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\("; # (
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "H"; # H
    $rc .= chr(oct(2)); # \\002
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "H"; # H
    $rc .= chr(oct(3)); # \\003
  } # %;

  return $rc;
}
',

sub {

           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= chr(oct(16)); # \\016
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= chr(oct(17)); # \\017
  } # %;

    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\("; # (
    $rc .= "8"; # 8

    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\("; # (
    $rc .= "\\}"; # }
  }

  return $rc;
}

#
# Stub version of: \\E%%!0\\ETF4%?%p1%{0}%=%t0%e%p1%{1}%=%t4%e%p1%{2}%=%t3%e%p1%{3}%=%t5%e%p1%{4}%=%t2%e%p1%{5}%=%t6%e%p1%{6}%=%t7%e1%;%?%p2%{125}%<%t0%e%p2%{250}%<%tA2%e%p2%{375}%<%tA?%e%p2%{500}%<%tC8%e%p2%{625}%<%tD4%e%p2%{750}%<%tE1%e%p2%{875}%<%tE\\:%eF4%;%?%p3%{125}%<%t0%e%p3%{250}%<%tA2%e%p3%{375}%<%tA?%e%p3%{500}%<%tC8%e%p3%{625}%<%tD4%e%p3%{750}%<%tE1%e%p3%{875}%<%tE\\:%eF4%;%?%p4%{125}%<%t0%e%p4%{250}%<%tA2%e%p4%{375}%<%tA?%e%p4%{500}%<%tC8%e%p4%{625}%<%tD4%e%p4%{750}%<%tE1%e%p4%{875}%<%tE\\:%eF4%;\\E%%!1
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= \'%\'; # %%
  $rc .= "\\!"; # !
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "T"; # T
  $rc .= "F"; # F
  $rc .= "4"; # 4
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "0"; # 0
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "3"; # 3
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 3); # %{3}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "2"; # 2
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 5); # %{5}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t

           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 65); # %{65}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 68); # %{68}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 72); # %{72}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 80); # %{80}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\>"; # >
    $rc .= "A"; # A
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\<"; # <
    $rc .= "\\@"; # @
  } # %;

  return $rc;
}

              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);

    $rc .= "\\<"; # <
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 13); # %{13}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\="; # =
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 14); # %{14}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "6"; # 6
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\?"; # ?
  } # ,
  return $rc;
}

  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [

  $rc .= "6"; # 6
  $rc .= "\\;"; # ;

  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  $rc .= "\\;"; # ;

           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           push(@iparam, 250); # %{250}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
              push(@iparam, 500); # %{500}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 16); # %{16}

              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 32); # %{32}
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, 48); # %{48}
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, 250); # %{250}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}

              push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
              push(@iparam, 500); # %{500}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
              push(@iparam, 750); # %{750}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, 12); # %{12}
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           push(@iparam, 250); # %{250}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<

         }) { # %t

              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<

         }) { # %t

  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, 3); # %{3}

  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+

# Stub version of: %?%p8%t\\E)%e\\E(%;%?%p9%t\\EcE%e\\EcD%;\\EG%{48}%?%p2%t%{8}%|%;%?%p1%p3%|%p6%|%t%{4}%|%;%?%p4%t%{2}%|%;%?%p1%p5%|%t%{64}%|%;%?%p7%t%{1}%|%;%c
#
sub {

  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible

  my $rc = \'\';

  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[7]); # %p8
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\)"; # )
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\("; # (
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E

    $rc .= "E"; # E
  }

    $rc .= "c"; # c

  $rc .= "G"; # G

  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|

#
# Stub version of: \\E[0%?%p1%p6%|%t;1%;%?%p2%t;4%;%?%p1%p3%|%t;7%;%?%p4%t;5%;m%?%p9%t\\016%e\\017%;$<100>

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "1"; # 1
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "7"; # 7
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
  } # %;

           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);

  }

  $rc .= "0"; # 0

# Stub version of: %?%p1%p2%|%p3%|%p6%|%p7%|%t\\026\\001%?%p7%t%{128}%e%{0}%?%p1%t%{112}%|%;%?%p2%t%{1}%|%;%?%p3%t%{112}%|%;%?%p6%t%{16}%|%;%;%c%;%?%p4%t\\026\\002%;
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= chr(oct(26)); # \\026
    $rc .= chr(oct(1)); # \\001
    if (do { # %?
             push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
             pop(@iparam);
           }) { # %t
      push(@iparam, 128); # %{128}
    }
    else { # %e
      push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}
      if (do { # %?
               push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
               pop(@iparam);
             }) { # %t
        push(@iparam, 112); # %{112}
        push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
      } # %;
      if (do { # %?
               push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
               pop(@iparam);
             }) { # %t
        push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
        push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
      } # %;
      if (do { # %?
               push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
               pop(@iparam);
             }) { # %t
        push(@iparam, 112); # %{112}
        push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
      } # %;
      if (do { # %?
               push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
               pop(@iparam);
             }) { # %t
        push(@iparam, 16); # %{16}
        push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
      } # %;
    } # %;
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= chr(oct(26)); # \\026
    $rc .= chr(oct(2)); # \\002
  } # %;

  return $rc;
}

# Stub version of: \\036A%p1%?%p1%{8}%<%t%{2}%&%?%p1%{1}%&%t%{4}%|%;%?%p1%{4}%&%t%{1}%|%;%;%{48}%+%c

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1

           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<

#
# Stub version of: \\E%%\\E(%?%p5%p8%|%t\\E)%;%?%p9%t\\E$%;\\EG%{48}%?%p7%t%{1}%+%;%?%p4%t%{2}%+%;%?%p3%p1%|%t%{4}%+%;%?%p2%t%{8}%+%;%c

  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= \'%\'; # %%
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\("; # (
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           push(@iparam, $param[7]); # %p8
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\)"; # )
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\$"; # $
  } # %;
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "G"; # G
  push(@iparam, 48); # %{48}
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3

           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           pop(@iparam);

    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c

  return $rc;
}

# Stub version of: %?%p1%{19}%=%t\\E\\023\\021%e%p1%{32}%<%t\\E%p1%c%e%p1%{127}%=%t\\E\\177%e%p1%c%;

sub {

  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;

  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 19); # %{19}

    $rc .= chr(oct(177)); # \\177

  else { # %e

  } # %;

           pop(@iparam);

  }

# Stub version of: \\E[%i%p1%d;%p2%dr$<100>
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  map {$param[$_]++} (0..$#param); # %i
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
  push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  $rc .= "r"; # r
  $rc .= "\\$"; # $
  $rc .= "\\<"; # <
  $rc .= "1"; # 1
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  $rc .= "\\>"; # >

  return $rc;
}

#
# Stub version of: %?%p1%{10}%=%t\\E[w%e%p1%{12}%=%t\\E[2w%e%p1%{5}%=%t\\E[5w%e%p1%{13}%=%p1%{14}%=%O%t\\E[3w%e%p1%{16}%=%p1%{17}%=%O%t\\E[4w%e%p1%{6}%=%t\\E[6w%e%p1%{7}%=%t\\E[7w%e%p1%{8}%=%t\\E[8w%;

sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 10); # %{10}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "w"; # w
  } # %;
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 12); # %{12}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "2"; # 2
    $rc .= "w"; # w
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 5); # %{5}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
    $rc .= "w"; # w
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 13); # %{13}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=

              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "3"; # 3
    $rc .= "w"; # w

              push(@iparam, 17); # %{17}

              push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) || pop(@iparam)); # %O
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
    $rc .= "w"; # w

  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\<"; # <
    push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
    push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
    if (do { # %?
             push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
             push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
             push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
             pop(@iparam);
           }) { # %t
      push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
      push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
    } # %;
    if (do { # %?
             push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
             push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
             push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
             pop(@iparam);
           }) { # %t
      push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
      push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
    } # %;
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $staticp->[3]); # %gD
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "2"; # 2
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $staticp->[20]); # %gU
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $staticp->[1]); # %gB
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $staticp->[17]); # %gR
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "7"; # 7
  } # %;
  $rc .= "m"; # m

  return $rc;
}
',

    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|

           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, $staticp->[2]); # %gC

    push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}

             push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1

          '\\E[%?%p1%{8}%<%t%p1%{40}%+%e%p1%{92}%+%;%dm' => '
#
# Stub version of: \\E[%?%p1%{8}%<%t%p1%{40}%+%e%p1%{92}%+%;%dm
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
    push(@iparam, 40); # %{40}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
    push(@iparam, 92); # %{92}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  $rc .= "m"; # m

  return $rc;
}

  $rc .= "W"; # W
  $rc .= chr(oct(36)); # \\036
  $rc .= "F"; # F
  $rc .= "J"; # J
  $rc .= chr(oct(36)); # \\036
  $rc .= "F"; # F
  $rc .= \'^\'; # \\^
  $rc .= chr(oct(36)); # \\036
  $rc .= "F"; # F
  $rc .= "X"; # X
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  $rc .= "4"; # 4
  $rc .= "\\?"; # ?
  $rc .= chr(oct(36)); # \\036
  $rc .= "F"; # F
  $rc .= "\\]"; # ]
  $rc .= chr(oct(36)); # \\036
  $rc .= "O"; # O
  $rc .= chr(oct(36)); # \\036
  $rc .= "F"; # F
  $rc .= "S"; # S
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  $rc .= "0"; # 0

  return $rc;
}

          '%?%p1%p3%|%t\\E`6\\E)%e%p5%p8%|%t\\E`7\\E)%e\\E(%;%?%p9%t\\EH\\002%e\\EH\\003%;' => '
#
# Stub version of: %?%p1%p3%|%t\\E`6\\E)%e%p5%p8%|%t\\E`7\\E)%e\\E(%;%?%p9%t\\EH\\002%e\\EH\\003%;
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\`"; # `
    $rc .= "6"; # 6
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\)"; # )
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
              push(@iparam, $param[7]); # %p8
              push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\`"; # `
    $rc .= "7"; # 7
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\)"; # )
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\("; # (
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "H"; # H
    $rc .= chr(oct(2)); # \\002
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "H"; # H
    $rc .= chr(oct(3)); # \\003
  } # %;

  return $rc;
}

    $rc .= "\\("; # (
    $rc .= "0"; # 0

    $rc .= "\\("; # (
    $rc .= "B"; # B
  } # %;

  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible

  $rc .= "4"; # 4

  push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}

  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 7); # %{7}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x > $y); } # %>
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "2"; # 2
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
  } # %;
  $rc .= "m"; # m

  return $rc;

          '\\020%p1%{10}%/%{16}%*%p1%{10}%m%+%Pc%?%{17}%gc%=%{19}%gc%=%|%gc%!%|%t%{1}%gc%+%c%{8}%e%gc%;%c' => '
#
# Stub version of: \\020%p1%{10}%/%{16}%*%p1%{10}%m%+%Pc%?%{17}%gc%=%{19}%gc%=%|%gc%!%|%t%{1}%gc%+%c%{8}%e%gc%;%c
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= chr(oct(20)); # \\020
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, 10); # %{10}
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $y ? int($x / $y) : 0); } # %/
  push(@iparam, 16); # %{16}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) * pop(@iparam)); # %*
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, 10); # %{10}
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $y ? int($x % $y) : 0); } # %m
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $dynamicp->[2] = pop(@iparam); # %Pc
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, 17); # %{17}
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           push(@iparam, 19); # %{19}
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
           push(@iparam, ! pop(@iparam)); # %!
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c

  return $rc;
}

# Stub version of: \\E&d%{0}%Pa%?%p4%t%{1}%ga%+%Pa%;%?%p1%p3%|%p6%|%t%{2}%ga%+%Pa%;%?%p2%p6%|%t%{4}%ga%+%Pa%;%?%p1%p5%|%t%{8}%ga%+%Pa%;%?%p7%t%?%ga%ts%ga%{64}%+%e%{83}%;%e%?%ga%t%ga%{64}%+%e%{64}%;%;%c

  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\&"; # &
  $rc .= "d"; # d
  push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}
  $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1

           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|

    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa

      push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
      push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}

    else { # %e

# Stub version of: \\013%p1%{32}%+%c\\020%p2%{10}%/%{16}%*%p2%{10}%m%+%Pc%?%{17}%gc%=%{19}%gc%=%|%gc%!%|%t%{1}%gc%+%c%{8}%e%gc%;%c

  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= chr(oct(13)); # \\013

  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  $rc .= chr(oct(20)); # \\020
  push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
  push(@iparam, 10); # %{10}
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $y ? int($x / $y) : 0); } # %/
  push(@iparam, 16); # %{16}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) * pop(@iparam)); # %*
  push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
  push(@iparam, 10); # %{10}
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $y ? int($x % $y) : 0); } # %m
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $dynamicp->[2] = pop(@iparam); # %Pc
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, 17); # %{17}
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           push(@iparam, 19); # %{19}
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
           push(@iparam, ! pop(@iparam)); # %!
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[2]); # %gc
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c

  return $rc;
}

  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "8"; # 8
  } # %;
  $rc .= "m"; # m
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= chr(oct(16)); # \\016
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= chr(oct(17)); # \\017
  } # %;
  $rc .= "\\$"; # $
  $rc .= "\\<"; # <
  $rc .= "2"; # 2
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  $rc .= "\\>"; # >

  return $rc;
}

           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5

         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[7]); # %p8
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\)"; # )
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "c"; # c
    $rc .= "E"; # E
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "c"; # c
    $rc .= "D"; # D
  } # %;

  return $rc;
}
',

#
# Stub version of: \\E&f0a%p1%dk%p2%l%Pa%?%ga%t%ga%d%e1%;d3L%?%ga%!%t%{32}%c%;%p2%s\\E%{111}%p1%+%c\\r
#

  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\&"; # &
  $rc .= "f"; # f
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  $rc .= "a"; # a
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  $rc .= "k"; # k
  push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
  $rc .= "\\%"; # %
  $rc .= "l"; # l
  $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "1"; # 1
  } # %;
  $rc .= "d"; # d
  $rc .= "3"; # 3
  $rc .= "L"; # L
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
           push(@iparam, ! pop(@iparam)); # %!
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 32); # %{32}
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  } # %;
  push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%s\', pop(@iparam)); # %s
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  push(@iparam, 111); # %{111}
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  $rc .= "\\r"; # \\r

# Stub version of: \\E&d%{0}%Pa%?%p4%t%{1}%ga%+%Pa%;%?%p1%p3%|%p6%|%t%{2}%ga%+%Pa%;%?%p2%p6%|%t%{4}%ga%+%Pa%;%?%p1%p5%|%t%{8}%ga%+%Pa%;%?%p7%t%?%ga%ts%ga%{64}%+%e%{83}%;%e%?%ga%t%ga%{64}%+%e%{64}%;%;%c%?%p9%t\\016%e\\017%;

  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\&"; # &
  $rc .= "d"; # d
  push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}
  $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);

    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);

    if (do { # %?
             push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
             pop(@iparam);
           }) { # %t
      $rc .= "s"; # s
      push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
      push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
      push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    }
    else { # %e
      push(@iparam, 83); # %{83}
    } # %;
  }
  else { # %e
    if (do { # %?
             push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
             pop(@iparam);

      push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
      push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
      push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+

    else { # %e
      push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
    } # %;

  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= chr(oct(16)); # \\016
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= chr(oct(17)); # \\017
  } # %;

#
# Stub version of: \\024%p1%{24}%+%c%p2%p2%?%{32}%>%t%{48}%+%;%{80}%+%c
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= chr(oct(24)); # \\024
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, 24); # %{24}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
  push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2

           push(@iparam, 32); # %{32}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x > $y); } # %>

    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+

  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c

#
# Stub version of: \\E[4%?%p1%{1}%=%t4%e%p1%{3}%=%t6%e%p1%{4}%=%t1%e%p1%{6}%=%t3%e%p1%d%;m

  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  $rc .= "4"; # 4
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 3); # %{3}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "6"; # 6
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "1"; # 1
  }

              push(@iparam, 6); # %{6}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);

    $rc .= "3"; # 3
  }
  else { # %e

  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\]"; # ]
  $rc .= "P"; # P
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 9); # %{9}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x > $y); } # %>
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
    push(@iparam, 10); # %{10}
    { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x - $y); } # %-
    push(@iparam, "a"); # %\'a\'
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  } # %;

  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) * pop(@iparam)); # %*
  push(@iparam, 1000); # %{1000}
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $y ? int($x / $y) : 0); } # %/

           pop(@iparam);

    push(@iparam, 10); # %{10}
    { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x - $y); } # %-
    push(@iparam, "a"); # %\'a\'

          '\\E[3%?%p1%{1}%=%t4%e%p1%{3}%=%t6%e%p1%{4}%=%t1%e%p1%{6}%=%t3%e%p1%d%;m' => '
#
# Stub version of: \\E[3%?%p1%{1}%=%t4%e%p1%{3}%=%t6%e%p1%{4}%=%t1%e%p1%{6}%=%t3%e%p1%d%;m
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  $rc .= "3"; # 3
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 3); # %{3}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "6"; # 6
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "1"; # 1
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 6); # %{6}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "3"; # 3
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  } # %;
  $rc .= "m"; # m

  return $rc;
}

  my @iparam = @param;

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<

  }
  else { # %e

  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&

         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
           pop(@iparam);

#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           pop(@iparam);

    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "7"; # 7

#
# Stub version of: \\036FB%?%p1%t%p1%2.2X1%;%p2%p1%-%{1}%+%2.2X1%?%{23}%p2%>%t001%;\\036FX%p3%2.2X%p4%2.2X

  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= chr(oct(36)); # \\036
  $rc .= "F"; # F
  $rc .= "B"; # B
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%2.2X\', pop(@iparam)); # %2.2X
    $rc .= "1"; # 1

  push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x - $y); } # %-
  push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%2.2X\', pop(@iparam)); # %2.2X
  $rc .= "1"; # 1
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, 23); # %{23}
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x > $y); } # %>
           pop(@iparam);

    $rc .= "0"; # 0
    $rc .= "1"; # 1

  $rc .= "F"; # F
  $rc .= "X"; # X

sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "0"; # 0
    $rc .= "t"; # t
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "1"; # 1
    $rc .= "t"; # t
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "2"; # 2
    $rc .= "t"; # t
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "3"; # 3
    $rc .= "t"; # t
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);

    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "7"; # 7
    $rc .= "m"; # m

  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\["; # [
    $rc .= "m"; # m

    push(@iparam, 76); # %{76}

  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 3); # %{3}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 72); # %{72}
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 5); # %{5}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 68); # %{68}
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 6); # %{6}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);

              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 7); # %{7}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "G"; # G
  push(@iparam, $staticp->[2]); # %gC
  push(@iparam, $staticp->[0]); # %gA

  push(@iparam, 48); # %{48}

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E

    $rc .= "5"; # 5

    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "2"; # 2
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[5]); # %p6
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "1"; # 1
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "8"; # 8
  } # %;
  $rc .= "\\+"; # +
  $rc .= "m"; # m
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= chr(oct(16)); # \\016
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= chr(oct(17)); # \\017
  } # %;

  return $rc;
}

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1

#

  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "b"; # b
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 0); # %{0}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\?"; # ?
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 7); # %{7}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=

    $rc .= "0"; # 0

              push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
              push(@iparam, 15); # %{15}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "7"; # 7
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
    push(@iparam, 48); # %{48}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c

           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "7"; # 7
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "5"; # 5
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "8"; # 8
  } # %;
  $rc .= "m"; # m
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\("; # (
    $rc .= "0"; # 0
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\("; # (
    $rc .= "B"; # B
  } # %;

  return $rc;
}
',

#
# Stub version of: \\E[0;%?%p1%{11}%<%t%\'\\:\'%e%?%p1%{13}%<%t%\'z\'%e%?%p1%{23}%<%t%\'G\'%e%?%p1%{25}%<%t%\'p\'%e%?%p1%\'#\'%<%t%\'E\'%e%?%p1%\'%\'%<%t%\'f\'%e%?%p1%\'/\'%<%t%\'C\'%e%{92}%;%;%;%;%;%;%;%p1%+%d;%p2"%s"p
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  $rc .= "0"; # 0
  $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 11); # %{11}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, \':\'); # %\'\\:\'
  }
  else { # %e
    if (do { # %?
             push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
             push(@iparam, 13); # %{13}
             { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
             pop(@iparam);
           }) { # %t
      push(@iparam, "z"); # %\'z\'
    }
    else { # %e
      if (do { # %?
               push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
               push(@iparam, 23); # %{23}
               { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
               pop(@iparam);
             }) { # %t
        push(@iparam, "G"); # %\'G\'
      }
      else { # %e
        if (do { # %?
                 push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
                 push(@iparam, 25); # %{25}
                 { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
                 pop(@iparam);
               }) { # %t
          push(@iparam, "p"); # %\'p\'
        }
        else { # %e
          if (do { # %?
                   push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
                   push(@iparam, "\\#"); # %\'#\'
                   { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
                   pop(@iparam);
                 }) { # %t
            push(@iparam, "E"); # %\'E\'
          }
          else { # %e
            if (do { # %?
                     push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
                     push(@iparam, "\\%"); # %\'%\'
                     { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
                     pop(@iparam);
                   }) { # %t
              push(@iparam, "f"); # %\'f\'
            }
            else { # %e
              if (do { # %?
                       push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
                       push(@iparam, "\\/"); # %\'/\'
                       { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
                       pop(@iparam);
                     }) { # %t
                push(@iparam, "C"); # %\'C\'
              }
              else { # %e
                push(@iparam, 92); # %{92}
              } # %;
            } # %;
          } # %;
        } # %;
      } # %;
    } # %;
  } # %;
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
  push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
  $rc .= "\\""; # "
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%s\', pop(@iparam)); # %s
  $rc .= "\\""; # "
  $rc .= "p"; # p

  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  $rc .= "5"; # 5
  $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
  $rc .= "\\>"; # >
  $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
  $rc .= "1"; # 1
  $rc .= "2"; # 2
  $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
  $rc .= "1"; # 1
  $rc .= "8"; # 8
  $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
  $rc .= "\\?"; # ?
  $rc .= "\\<"; # <
  $rc .= "l"; # l
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  $rc .= "\\="; # =
  $rc .= "h"; # h
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "P"; # P
  $rc .= "1"; # 1
  $rc .= "s"; # s
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\\\"; # \\
  $rc .= "\\\\"; # \\

  $rc .= "p"; # p

#
# Stub version of: %p1%{8}%/%{6}%*%{3}%+\\E[%d%p1%{8}%m%Pa%?%ga%{1}%=%t4%e%ga%{3}%=%t6%e%ga%{4}%=%t1%e%ga%{6}%=%t3%e%ga%d%;m
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $y ? int($x / $y) : 0); } # %/
  push(@iparam, 6); # %{6}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) * pop(@iparam)); # %*
  push(@iparam, 3); # %{3}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) + pop(@iparam)); # %+
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
  { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $y ? int($x % $y) : 0); } # %m
  $dynamicp->[0] = pop(@iparam); # %Pa
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
           push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
              push(@iparam, 3); # %{3}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "6"; # 6
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
              push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "1"; # 1
  }
  elsif (do { # %e
              push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
              push(@iparam, 6); # %{6}
              { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x == $y); } # %=
              pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "3"; # 3
  }
  else { # %e
    push(@iparam, $dynamicp->[0]); # %ga
    $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  } # %;
  $rc .= "m"; # m

  return $rc;
}

#
# Stub version of: \\E[%?%p1%{8}%<%t4%e=%;%p1%{2}%&%?%p1%{1}%&%t%{4}%|%;%?%p1%{4}%&%t%{1}%|%;%d%?%gD%t;2%;%?%gU%t;4%;%?%gB%t;5%;%?%gR%t;7%;m
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "\\["; # [
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
           { my $y = pop(@iparam); my $x = pop(@iparam); push(@iparam, $x < $y); } # %<
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "4"; # 4
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\="; # =
  } # %;
  push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
  push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
  push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) & pop(@iparam)); # %&
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%d\', pop(@iparam)); # %d
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $staticp->[3]); # %gD
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "2"; # 2
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $staticp->[20]); # %gU
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\;"; # ;
    $rc .= "4"; # 4

    $rc .= "5"; # 5
  } # %;

           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t

    $rc .= "7"; # 7
  } # %;
  $rc .= "m"; # m

}

#
# Stub version of: %?%p8%t\\E)%e\\E(%;%?%p9%t\\EH\\002%e\\EH\\003%;\\EG%{48}%?%p2%t%{8}%|%;%?%p1%p3%|%t%{4}%|%;%?%p4%t%{2}%|%;%?%p1%p5%|%t%{64}%|%;%?%p7%t%{1}%|%;%c
#
sub {
  my ($self, $dynamicp, $staticp, @param) = @_;
  # Initialized with @param to be termcap compatible
  my @iparam = @param;
  my $rc = \'\';

  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[7]); # %p8
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\)"; # )
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "\\("; # (
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[8]); # %p9
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "H"; # H
    $rc .= chr(oct(2)); # \\002
  }
  else { # %e
    $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
    $rc .= "H"; # H
    $rc .= chr(oct(3)); # \\003
  } # %;
  $rc .= "\\e"; # \\E
  $rc .= "G"; # G
  push(@iparam, 48); # %{48}
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[1]); # %p2
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 8); # %{8}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[2]); # %p3
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 4); # %{4}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[3]); # %p4
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 2); # %{2}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[0]); # %p1
           push(@iparam, $param[4]); # %p5
           push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 64); # %{64}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  if (do { # %?
           push(@iparam, $param[6]); # %p7
           pop(@iparam);
         }) { # %t
    push(@iparam, 1); # %{1}
    push(@iparam, pop(@iparam) | pop(@iparam)); # %|
  } # %;
  $rc .= sprintf(\'%c\', pop(@iparam)); # %c

  return $rc;
}
